# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:18
translate french mrsmcgee10a_fa520e80:

    # "As we work on our assignments in English class, Mrs. McGee comes by my desk and leans down to whisper in my ear."
    "Alors que nous travaillons sur nos devoirs en cours d'anglais, Mme McGee s'approche de mon bureau et se penche pour me chuchoter à l'oreille."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:19
translate french mrsmcgee10a_d9b1882f:

    # et "[pcname], would you stay after class a few moments. There's something I'd like to discuss with you."
    et "[pcname], pourrais-tu rester quelques instants après le cours ? J'aimerais discuter de quelque chose avec toi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:20
translate french mrsmcgee10a_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Oui, madame."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:23
translate french mrsmcgee10a_cc0f4023:

    # "Wonder what she could want to talk about this time? Whatever it is, I'm excited to find out."
    "Je me demande de quoi elle veut bien me parler cette fois-ci ? Quoi qu'il en soit, j'ai hâte de le découvrir."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:26
translate french mrsmcgee10a_6facc3ac:

    # "After the rest of the classroom empties, Mrs. McGee shuts the door and sits on her desk."
    "Une fois la classe vide, Mme McGee ferme la porte et s’assoit sur son bureau."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:27
translate french mrsmcgee10a_1e1882e3:

    # et "Would you like to come over to my house for dinner tonight?"
    et "Voudrais-tu venir dîner chez moi ce soir ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:28
translate french mrsmcgee10a_9bc190a8:

    # pc "Dinner?"
    pc "Dîner ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:29
translate french mrsmcgee10a_d5ef02f0:

    # et "Yes, if you'd like. I make a very nice kasha. I promise you will have a good time."
    et "Oui, si tu veux. Je fais un très bon kasha. Je te promets que tu passeras un bon moment."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:34
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_ececefc2:

    # et "Good, then I will see you this evening. Say, around 6:30?"
    et "Très bien, alors je te verrai ce soir. Disons, vers 18 h 30 ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:35
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_36ffe6b6:

    # "She hands me a note with her address on it."
    "Elle me tend un bout de papier avec son adresse."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:36
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_ad15b3ba:

    # pc "I'll be there. Should I bring anything?"
    pc "J'y serai. Je dois apporter quelque chose ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:37
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_4ee87fdf:

    # et "Just you. That's all I need."
    et "Juste toi. C'est tout ce dont j'ai besoin."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:38
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_696181f3:

    # pc "Okay then, see you tonight."
    pc "D'accord, à ce soir alors."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:39
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_dd6a1a96:

    # et "Goodbye, [pcname]."
    et "Au revoir, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:43
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_3f5db218:

    # "I leave her class, looking forward to whatever is going to happen tonight. It definitely seems like she wants more than to just eat dinner with me."
    "Je quitte sa classe, impatient de voir ce qui va se passer ce soir. On dirait bien qu'elle veut plus qu'un simple dîner avec moi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:44
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_dc3258ef:

    # "And I want more than that with her too."
    "Et moi aussi, je veux plus que ça avec elle."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:51
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_eea40836:

    # et "Oh. Maybe some other time then."
    et "Oh. Peut-être une autre fois alors."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:52
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:53
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_577e28d7:

    # et "Have a good day, [pcname]."
    et "Passe une bonne journée, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:54
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_eb61ef6e:

    # pc "You too."
    pc "Toi aussi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:57
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_b142bee1:

    # "I leave and go on with the rest of my day. I wonder why I turned that down? Maybe I'm not really interested in Mrs. McGee at all."
    "Je pars et je continue ma journée. Je me demande pourquoi j’ai refusé ça ? Peut-être que Mme McGee ne m’intéresse pas vraiment."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:63
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_d4a7d900:

    # et "Oh, it's a type of soup or porridge, with cereal in it."
    et "Oh, c’est une sorte de soupe ou de porridge, avec des céréales dedans."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:64
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_3d903830:

    # pc "Like Frosted Flakes or something?"
    pc "Comme des Frosted Flakes ou quelque chose comme ça ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:65
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_230a666c:

    # et "Um, no... not like Frosted Flakes."
    et "Euh, non… pas comme des Frosted Flakes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:66
translate french mrsmcgee10menu_a3518e13:

    # et "It's good. You will like it. So what do you think? Will you come?"
    et "C'est bon. Tu vas aimer. Alors, qu'en penses-tu ? Tu viens ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:76
translate french mrsmcgee10_a5aa248c:

    # "After I leave work, I drive home, take a quick shower, and change clothes, then head over to the address that Mrs. McGee gave me."
    "Après le travail, je rentre chez moi en voiture, je prends une douche rapide, je me change, puis je me rends à l'adresse que Mme McGee m'a donnée."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:79
translate french mrsmcgee10_c2171e40:

    # "I pull up into the driveway and park. She lives in a small house in the suburbs, much like my own."
    "Je m'engage dans l'allée et je me gare. Elle vit dans une petite maison en banlieue, un peu comme la mienne."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:80
translate french mrsmcgee10_c58d627f:

    # "A little nervous about how things are going to go tonight, I take a deep breath, then step out and walk up to the door."
    "Un peu nerveux à l’idée de comment les choses vont se passer ce soir, je prends une grande inspiration, puis je sors de la voiture et me dirige vers la porte."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:83
translate french mrsmcgee10_0b66d801:

    # "When I get to the door, I raise my hand to knock..."
    "Quand j’arrive à la porte, je lève la main pour frapper…"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:85
translate french mrsmcgee10_0a429c3d:

    # "But before my knuckles touch wood, the door swings open and Mr. McGee is standing there with a big smile on his face."
    "Mais avant que mes jointures ne touchent le bois, la porte s’ouvre et M. McGee se tient là, un grand sourire aux lèvres."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:86
translate french mrsmcgee10_bda45b99:

    # mrmg "[pcname]! I'm so glad you came! Come on in!"
    mrmg "[pcname]! Je suis tellement content que tu sois venu ! Entre !"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:89
translate french mrsmcgee10_f8f82946:

    # "I walk in and stand in the foyer, a little awkward. The place smells amazing - that savory smell of grilled onions with an underhint of bacon."
    "J'entre et je reste debout dans le hall, un peu mal à l'aise. Ça sent incroyablement bon ici – cette odeur savoureuse d'oignons grillés avec une touche de bacon."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:90
translate french mrsmcgee10_fb665e30:

    # pc "Thank you for inviting me, Mr. McGee."
    pc "Merci de m'avoir invité, M. McGee."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:91
translate french mrsmcgee10_5ba2ce58:

    # mrmg "Oh that's going to be weird if you keep calling me Mister. Call me Pete, okay?"
    mrmg "Oh, ça va être bizarre si tu continues à m'appeler « Monsieur ». Appelle-moi Pete, d'accord ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:92
translate french mrsmcgee10_845da3d6:

    # pc "Alright, Pete."
    pc "D'accord, Pete."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:94
translate french mrsmcgee10_3561000e:

    # mrmg "I think Edie's done cooking and is in the bedroom getting dressed now, if you want to join me in the dining room, we can wait for her there."
    mrmg "Je crois qu’Edie a fini de cuisiner et qu’elle est en train de s’habiller dans la chambre. Si tu veux me rejoindre dans la salle à manger, on peut l’attendre là-bas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:95
translate french mrsmcgee10_74dad17c:

    # pc "Okay, sure."
    pc "D’accord, bien sûr."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:98
translate french mrsmcgee10_ce18fa39:

    # mrmg "Are you okay? You seem a little nervous."
    mrmg "Ça va ? Tu as l’air un peu nerveuse."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:99
translate french mrsmcgee10_4c567549:

    # pc "I am... this is a little weird."
    pc "Je suis… c’est un peu bizarre."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:100
translate french mrsmcgee10_f000a834:

    # mrmg "It's fine, I promise. We both like you and just wanted to have dinner and talk a bit."
    mrmg "Tout va bien, je te le promets. On t’apprécie tous les deux et on voulait juste dîner et discuter un peu."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:101
translate french mrsmcgee10_760593d6:

    # mrmg "And we'll just leave it at that if you don't want to take it any further."
    mrmg "Et on en restera là si tu ne veux pas aller plus loin."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:102
translate french mrsmcgee10_67b4f891:

    # mrmg "At the very least, you'll get some good food. Edie's kasha is amazing."
    mrmg "Au moins, tu vas bien manger. Le kasha d’Edie est incroyable."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:103
translate french mrsmcgee10_8e1808a3:

    # pc "Mrs. McGee's name is Edie?"
    pc "Mme McGee s’appelle Edie ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:104
translate french mrsmcgee10_6ed863ba:

    # mrmg "Well, Eden. But I call her Edie."
    mrmg "Eh bien, Eden. Mais je l’appelle Edie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:107
translate french mrsmcgee10_3ea2e3a2:

    # mrmg "There she is, my beautiful wife."
    mrmg "La voilà, ma magnifique femme."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:108
translate french mrsmcgee10_ce59dba2:

    # pc "Wow."
    pc "Waouh."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:109
translate french mrsmcgee10_6c592216:

    # et "Hello, boys. Hitting it off in here?"
    et "Bonjour, les garçons. Ça se passe bien ici ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:110
translate french mrsmcgee10_11adb751:

    # mrmg "We were just talking about you."
    mrmg "On était justement en train de parler de toi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:111
translate french mrsmcgee10_0b1aa19c:

    # et "Oh yeah? I like that."
    et "Ah oui ? Ça me fait plaisir."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:112
translate french mrsmcgee10_fb640479:

    # et "I'm glad you made it, [pcname]."
    et "Je suis contente que tu sois venu, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:113
translate french mrsmcgee10_c8e5d523:

    # et "Are you two ready to eat?"
    et "Vous êtes prêts à manger ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:114
translate french mrsmcgee10_e9a44191:

    # mrmg "Absolutely. I'm starving."
    mrmg "Absolument. Je meurs de faim."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:117
translate french mrsmcgee10_99840180:

    # "She serves the kasha to us, putting a glass of white wine along with the bowls. Then she surprises me by sitting next to me instead of her husband."
    "Elle nous sert le kasha, en accompagnant les bols d'un verre de vin blanc. Puis elle me surprend en s'asseyant à côté de moi plutôt qu'à côté de son mari."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:118
translate french mrsmcgee10_1c875ad0:

    # et "I hope you enjoy. Kasha is one of my specialties."
    et "J'espère que ça te plaira. Le kasha est l'une de mes spécialités."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:119
translate french mrsmcgee10_d21d1a56:

    # pc "It smells delicious."
    pc "Ça sent délicieux."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:122
translate french mrsmcgee10_938106e2:

    # "I spoon a bite into my mouth, then a few more spoonfuls as well."
    "Je porte une cuillerée à ma bouche, puis quelques autres."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:123
translate french mrsmcgee10_57c039b1:

    # pc "Tastes delicious too. Wow, that's good."
    pc "C'est délicieux aussi. Waouh, c'est bon."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:124
translate french mrsmcgee10_c688553f:

    # et "I'm so glad you like it."
    et "Je suis ravie que ça te plaise."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:125
translate french mrsmcgee10_021eca64:

    # mrmg "I've never met anybody who didn't love Edie's cooking. It's one of the many things that she's incredible at."
    mrmg "Je n'ai jamais rencontré quelqu'un qui n'aimait pas la cuisine d'Edie. C'est l'une des nombreuses choses pour lesquelles elle est incroyable."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:126
translate french mrsmcgee10_43260e5f:

    # et "You're going to make me blush, honey."
    et "Tu vas me faire rougir, chérie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:127
translate french mrsmcgee10_da04860f:

    # mrmg "That's okay. You're gorgeous when you blush."
    mrmg "Ce n'est pas grave. Tu es magnifique quand tu rougis."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:130
translate french mrsmcgee10_2e788e2b:

    # mrmg "So, [pcname], we'd love to learn a bit more about you. Do you live with your parents?"
    mrmg "Alors, [pcname], on aimerait en savoir un peu plus sur toi. Tu vis avec tes parents ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:131
translate french mrsmcgee10_9f71a1fe:

    # "I spent the next few minutes telling them about my mom's death and my dad going missing, and Lisa and Suzy."
    "J'ai passé les minutes suivantes à leur parler de la mort de ma mère, de la disparition de mon père, ainsi que de Lisa et Suzy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:134
translate french mrsmcgee10_52df5a2c:

    # et "I had no idea you were going through all this. And you're still making straight A's in my class."
    et "Je ne savais pas du tout que tu traversais tout ça. Et pourtant, tu continues à avoir des 20/20 dans ma classe."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:135
translate french mrsmcgee10_6959b302:

    # et "I'm sorry you're having to deal with those things. It sounds like a hard situation."
    et "Je suis désolée que tu doives faire face à tout ça. Ça a l'air d'être une situation difficile."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:136
translate french mrsmcgee10_4f633b03:

    # pc "It is, sometimes. But things haven't been all bad. This dinner, for instance."
    pc "Ça l'est, parfois. Mais tout n'a pas été que négatif. Ce dîner, par exemple."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:137
translate french mrsmcgee10_a831879f:

    # et "I'm glad that I could make you feel a little better."
    et "Je suis contente d'avoir pu te remonter un peu le moral."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:140
translate french mrsmcgee10_1dd2ecf3:

    # mrmg "Do you have a girlfriend, [pcname]?"
    mrmg "Tu as une petite amie, [pcname] ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:143
translate french mrsmcgee10_ea5b0c28:

    # pc "Yeah, I do."
    pc "Oui, j'en ai une."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:144
translate french mrsmcgee10_5474e481:

    # mrmg "Are things serious?"
    mrmg "C'est sérieux entre vous ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:145
translate french mrsmcgee10_e01ed414:

    # pc "Pretty serious."
    pc "Assez sérieux."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:146
translate french mrsmcgee10_ce8a6513:

    # mrmg "I see."
    mrmg "Je vois."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:149
translate french mrsmcgee10_7e1bf495:

    # mrmg "Wow, that's hard to believe!"
    mrmg "Ouah, c'est dur à croire !"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:150
translate french mrsmcgee10_9d64452a:

    # pc "You think so?"
    pc "Tu crois ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:151
translate french mrsmcgee10_e1f479aa:

    # mrmg "I mean, you're kind of a stud! I figured you'd be drowning in college girls."
    mrmg "Je veux dire, t'es un vrai tombeur ! Je pensais que tu serais submergé par les étudiantes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:152
translate french mrsmcgee10_29fc5af6:

    # pc "Yeah, not so much."
    pc "Ouais, pas vraiment."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:153
translate french mrsmcgee10_f29811da:

    # mrmg "Well, you definitely caught Edie's attention at least."
    mrmg "Eh bien, t'as clairement attiré l'attention d'Edie, au moins."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:155
translate french mrsmcgee10_d867934a:

    # mrmg "Ha! That's what I figured."
    mrmg "Ha ! C'est ce que je me disais."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:156
translate french mrsmcgee10_c7cf6fcb:

    # mrmg "You're kind of a stud! I knew you'd be drowning in college girls."
    mrmg "T'es un vrai tombeur ! Je savais que tu serais submergé par les étudiantes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:157
translate french mrsmcgee10_64d17d06:

    # mrmg "You definitely caught Edie's attention."
    mrmg "T'as clairement attiré l'attention d'Edie."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:160
translate french mrsmcgee10_6ef17689:

    # "We chit chat a bit more while we finish our bowls. I eat every last drop."
    "On bavarde encore un peu pendant qu'on finit nos bols. Je mange jusqu'à la dernière miette."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:161
translate french mrsmcgee10_668c4331:

    # et "Did you get enough, dear?"
    et "Tu t'es bien régalé, mon chéri ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:162
translate french mrsmcgee10_b4599cf5:

    # "It takes me a moment to realize that she's asking me, not her husband."
    "Il me faut un moment pour réaliser qu'elle s'adresse à moi, pas à son mari."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:163
translate french mrsmcgee10_b4bade14:

    # pc "Oh yes, Mrs. McGee, thank you."
    pc "Oh oui, Mme McGee, merci."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:164
translate french mrsmcgee10_9d8d8515:

    # et "Call me Eden, please."
    et "Appelle-moi Eden, s'il te plaît."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:165
translate french mrsmcgee10_180bb07c:

    # pc "Okay, Eden."
    pc "D'accord, Eden."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:170
translate french mrsmcgee10_76f15013:

    # mrmg "I guess we should talk about the second reason we invited you over tonight, besides the food."
    mrmg "Je suppose qu'on devrait parler de la deuxième raison pour laquelle on t'a invité ce soir, à part le repas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:171
translate french mrsmcgee10_e18be8a3:

    # mrmg "My wife likes you, [pcname]. Since the beginning of the school year, you're all she talks about."
    mrmg "Ma femme t'apprécie, [pcname]. Depuis la rentrée scolaire, elle ne parle que de toi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:172
translate french mrsmcgee10_b3c66524:

    # mrmg "She lies in bed at night and tells me how much she wants to have sex with you."
    mrmg "Le soir, au lit, elle me dit à quel point elle a envie de coucher avec toi."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:175
translate french mrsmcgee10_399bdc0f:

    # pc "Really?"
    pc "Vraiment ?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:176
translate french mrsmcgee10_9880f614:

    # et "Yes."
    et "Oui."

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee10.rpy:179
translate french mrsmcgee10_546d48e6:

    # mrmg "My wife and I love each other very much. We are extremely happy in our relationship."
